    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash, then add the <strong>shredded kale</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until tender with a bite</p><p>Crumble in the <strong>Greek cheese</strong>, add the<strong> dried cranberries </strong>and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>cheesy filling</strong></p><p>Remove the pan from the heat and set aside</p>",
