    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the sweet potatoes from the oven and spoon the <strong>cheesy filling</strong> over the top</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>flaked almonds</strong> over and return the tray to the oven for a final 3-4 min</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p><p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>chopped parsley</strong>, <strong>diced onion</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>honey-Dijon dressing</strong> (save the rest for later!) to the <strong>couscous </strong>and stir everything together<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>herby couscous</strong></p>",
